	// - Generate shareable invite links
	// - Manage team growth
	// - Control organization access
	//
	// ### Examples
	//
	// - Create organization invite:
	//
	//	Generates a new invite link for the organization.
	//
	//	```yaml
	//	organizationId: "b0e12f6c-4c67-429d-a4a6-d9838b5da047"
	//	```
